TITLE: Defining a Basic Header Component in templ
DESCRIPTION: Example of defining a basic header component in a .templ file that takes a name parameter and renders it within an h1 tag inside a header element.
SOURCE: https://github.com/a-h/templ/blob/main/docs/docs/04-core-concepts/01-components.md#2025-04-18_snippet_0

LANGUAGE: templ
CODE:
```
package main

templ headerTemplate(name string) {
  <header data-testid="headerTemplate">
    <h1>{ name }</h1>
  </header>
}
```

