TITLE: HTTP Server with Parameterized templ Components and Status Codes
DESCRIPTION: Implementation of an HTTP server that uses parameterized templ components and demonstrates the use of templ.WithStatus to set HTTP status codes. This example shows how to pass fixed data to components.
SOURCE: https://github.com/a-h/templ/blob/main/docs/docs/05-server-side-rendering/01-creating-an-http-server-with-templ.md#2025-04-18_snippet_3

LANGUAGE: go
CODE:
```
package main

