TITLE: Live reload sequence diagram
DESCRIPTION: Mermaid sequence diagram illustrating the live reload process flow between browser, templ proxy, and application during the development cycle.
SOURCE: https://github.com/a-h/templ/blob/main/docs/docs/09-developer-tools/03-live-reload.md#2025-04-18_snippet_3

