TITLE: Configuring Tailwind CSS LSP for Templ in Neovim
DESCRIPTION: Lua configuration to set up the Tailwind CSS language server for Templ files in Neovim. This provides Tailwind CSS class autocompletion in Templ templates by mapping them to HTML.
