LANGUAGE: lua
CODE:
```
lspconfig.tailwindcss.setup({
    on_attach = on_attach,
    capabilities = capabilities,
    filetypes = { "templ", "astro", "javascript", "typescript", "react" },
    settings = {
      tailwindCSS = {
        includeLanguages = {
          templ = "html",
        },
      },
    },
})
```

